{"tid":2188020,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"保叔：李城絕對係降班大熱","createTime":"2020-09-04T03:57:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-29T16:36:33.000Z","uid":92376,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"9efbd90bf48cb67ee328dde7cc85abd678ce0810","tid":2188020,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T03:57:24.000Z","msg":"英超開季除了為大球會預測排名外，球評家都喜愛估計哪支球隊降班，前保加利亞球僮相信，因上季復賽大走樣而要轉戰歐霸的李斯特城應難逃一劫。<br />\n<br />\n李斯特城2016年曾擊敗阿仙奴奪得英超，當時觀看直播的保藉球僮相信李城季尾應保不住英超席位，箇中原因跟領隊有關。 <br />\n<br />\n「雖然李斯特城領隊羅渣士具備領導才能，但始終因為上季失利而心理陷入崩潰。而且會方季前放售多名球員，羅渣士未必能作出最好的應變。即使球隊簽入卡斯泰尼等球員，球隊的前景仍不甚樂觀。」保叔在其專欄寫道。 <br />\n<br />\n這名38歲前保加利亞球僮亦指出，季初賽程會將李斯特城推往深淵。「李斯特城頭3場將面對西布朗、般尼及曼城，相信極難取得分數。如果之後對韋斯咸的比賽也未能取勝，聯賽只是開始一個月，就會發現日子將極度難過，而他們亦缺乏足夠的經驗去處理這些問題。」"},{"pid":"70c754b49c411d95d68faa5df1e550a507be6176","tid":2188020,"uid":12628,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T03:59:18.000Z","msg":"球僮都有明叔🥴"},{"pid":"4b3e6a30bcb58b356733b5ca500a933efdbe6634","tid":2188020,"uid":218659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70c754b49c411d95d68faa5df1e550a507be6176","tid":2188020,"uid":12628,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T03:59:18.000Z","msg":"球僮都有明叔🥴"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:01:41.000Z","msg":"笑咗😂 仲諗緊邊個"},{"pid":"264897432363bd6c45b5339d5ffa19e2f7e8d310","tid":2188020,"uid":199081,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:03:01.000Z","msg":"唔樂觀<br />\n但點都唔會去到降班咁柒"},{"pid":"c0068a075910ec1205f1b49bd07d9b5461324bf3","tid":2188020,"uid":99700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:11:12.000Z","msg":"降班3隊 狼隊 列斯聯 李城"},{"pid":"f4225b459d7da299fcb0ec32337a0f665477c91e","tid":2188020,"uid":239336,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:16:47.000Z","msg":"吹大啲啦不如<br />\n白禮頓、富咸、西布朗降班李城都未降啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7b205dab8c75d93aeb6c6b52dcee3803f68423a","tid":2188020,"uid":92376,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4225b459d7da299fcb0ec32337a0f665477c91e","tid":2188020,"uid":239336,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:16:47.000Z","msg":"吹大啲啦不如<br />\n白禮頓、富咸、西布朗降班李城都未降啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:20:18.000Z","msg":"白禮頓降硬"},{"pid":"aa4cbd1d940ab1d38a68e30c599e1e30493cd415","tid":2188020,"uid":81273,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:22:37.000Z","msg":"華迪 泰利文斯 蘇恩祖 舒米高 麥迪臣 <br />\n你同我講降班"},{"pid":"fbcbb5ac20d1cd6b3f231a479d722f46e3edf19e","tid":2188020,"uid":360710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:49:35.000Z","msg":"真係尻吹都唔好咁大啊... 一大堆等降班都未到李城啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab877f3c1a4f9b4aef29abcc2eb9e4c0efbc5265","tid":2188020,"uid":47007,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T05:20:03.000Z","msg":"帶棗兒又名屈dee aka蜜糖人<br />\n不斷老屈李城唔掂兼降班<br />\n觸犯港區國安法<br />\n因為李城=泰國班主=泰國政府=中泰友好=中共=特區政府<br />\n<br />\n即係煽動他人認為特區政府唔掂兼出事"},{"pid":"2bcd7217c3dc33b3f7f9b74e62a649d5395769ac","tid":2188020,"uid":149607,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T05:22:28.000Z","msg":"阿仙奴降李城都未降啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86214c361590a8579b84304944342d27ae3d070c","tid":2188020,"uid":228851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T05:28:44.000Z","msg":"維拉 白禮頓 修咸頓 水晶宮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd157492c857c9774254ff9b78406202a13b311d","tid":2188020